s%20Angeles%20after%20hundreds%20of%20students%20started%20an%20occupation%20on%20the%20campus%20and%20raised%20%26quot%3Bfree%2C%20free%20Palestine%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20controversial%20slogans.%20This%20prompted%20the%20university%20to%20announce%20closing%20the%20campus%20to%20visitors.%20Classes%2C%20however%2C%20would%20continue%20here.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProtests%20have%20also%20erupted%20at%20Yale%2C%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%2C%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Brown.%20At%20Harvard%2C%20students%20have%20begun%20an%20encampment%20exercise%2C%20setting%20up%20tents%20on%20the%20campus.%20At%20a%20protest%20in%20New%20York%20University%2C%20over%20130%20people%20were%20arrested%20on%20Monday%20while%20another%20nine%20people%20were%20detained%20reportedly%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESeveral%20Jewish%20students'%20group%20have%20labelled%20these%20protests%20%26quot%3Bantisemitic%26quot%3B%2C%20claiming%20they%20are%20against%20Israel%20and%20Zionism%2C%20but%20pro-Palestinian%20protests%20differ%20with%20this%20conclusion.%20They%20claim%20being%20anti-Israel%20was%20not%20the%20same%20as%20anti-semitism%2C%20which%20means%20they%20hatred%20against%20Jews.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20condemned%20the%20US%20protests%20as%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bantisemitic%20mobs%20have%20taken%20over%20leading%20universities.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAnti-Semitism%20on%20campuses%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20what%20happened%20in%20German%20universities%20in%20the%201930s.%20The%20world%20cannot%20stand%20idly%20by%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20sharing%20a%20video%20message.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhite%20House%20spokeswoman%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%20played%20down%20the%20protests%20and%20said%20Biden%20backed%20free%20speech.%20She%20told%20reporters%20President%20Bide