ccused%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20allegedly%20helped%20him%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20cops%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20another%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20senior%20police%20officer%20Aman%20Yadav%2C%20Satish%20works%20as%20a%20bank%20manager%20in%20Delhi%20and%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20Sector%2062%20in%20Faridabad.%20His%20wife%20is%20a%20government%20employee.%20Bhupendra%2C%20who%20lived%20as%20a%20tenant%20in%20Satish's%20house%20till%20four%20months%20back%2C%20was%20out%20of%20work.%20He%20knew%20Satish's%20family%20was%20well-off%20and%20planned%20to%20kidnap%20him%20and%20demand%20ransom%2C%20said%20the%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20hatched%20by%20Bhupendra%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20Ravindra%2C%20his%20former%20colleague%20at%20a%20petrol%20pump%2C%20said%20police.%20Bhupendra%20and%20Ravindra%20recced%20the%20area%20near%20Satish's%20house%20for%20two-three%20days%20before%20the%20kidnapping.%20Having%20lived%20there%2C%20Bhupendra%20knew%20that%20the%20main%20door%20is%20not%20locked%2C%20even%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20he%20entered%20the%20house.%20Satish%20was%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20a%20friend.%20Bhupendra%20pointed%20a%20gun%20at%20them.%20When%20Satish's%20friend%20Amit%20tried%20to%20intervene%2C%20he%20hit%20him%20with%20a%20hammer%2C%20police%20said.%20Bhupendra%20took%20away%20the%20phones%20of%20Satish's%20wife%20and%20Amit.%20He%20also%20took%20Satish's%20car%20keys%20and%20wallet.%20On%20gunpoint%2C%20Satish%20was%20asked%20to%20get%20into%20his%20car%20and%20drive%20to%20Rohini.%20At%20Rohini%2C%20Ravindra%20joined%20Bhupendra.%20Satish's%20car%20was%20left%20there%20and%20the%20accused%20put%20him%20into%20a%20cab.%20His%20hands%20and%20feet%20were%20tied%2C%20mouth%20gagged%20and%20the%20rear%20seat%20partition%20used%20to%20hide%20him.%20The%20kidnappers%20refuelled%20the%20cab%20using%20Satish's%20credit%20card.%20The%20next%20stop%20was%20Himachal.%20Bhupendra's%20wife%20sat%20in%20the%20front%20to%20suggest%20that%20a%20family%20was%20in%20the%20car%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20Himachal%2C%20the%20kidnappers%20made%20the%20ransom%20call%20and%20demanded%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20from%20Satish's%20family.%20By%20now%2C%20police%20had%20been%20informed%20and%20six%20teams%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20track%20down%20the%20kidnappers%20and%20rescue%20Satish.%20Officers%20of%20the%20crime%20branch%20were%20present%20during%20the%20telephonic%20negotiations.%20When%20the%20family%20said%20they%20cannot%20pay%20Rs%2050%20lakh%2C%20Bhupendra%20settled%20for%205%20lakh.%20He%20asked%20them%20to%20transfer%20the%20amount%20to%20Satish's%20bank%20account.%20The%20family%20said%20they%20did%20not%20have%20the%20amount%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20but%20can%20arrange%20cash.%20Bhupendra%20asked%20them%20to%20transfer%201%20lakh%20to%20the%20account%20and%20arrange%20for%20the%20rest%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Bhupendra%20reached%20Keli%20bypass%20to%20collect%20the%20cash%20from%20Satish's%20wife.%20Once%20she%20handed%20over%20the%20money%2C%20he%20got%20into%20the%20cab%20in%20which%20he%20had%20come.%20The%20crime%20branch%20team%20was%20waiting%20and%20he%20was%20arrested.%20On%20questioning%2C%20he%20revealed%20that%20Satish%20had%20been%20shifted%20to%20Mathura%20and%20Ravindra%20was%20with%20him.%20Once%20he%20found%20out%20that%20Bhupendra%20had%20been%20arrested%2C%20Ravindra%20fled%20the%20Mathura%20hideout%20and%20police%20rescued%20Satish.%20He%20had%20been%20hit%20on%20the%20face%20with%20the%20pistol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhupendra%20has%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20no%20work%20for%20months%20now%20and%20needed%20money%2C%20and%20that%20led%20him%20to%20commit%20the%20crime.%20Police%20have%20recovered%20the%20cash%20Satish%20wife%20had%20handed%20over%20to%20Bhupendra%2C%20a%20pistol%2C%20a%20countrymade%20gun%2C%20bullets%2C%20and%20the%20car%20used%20in%20the%20crime.%20The%20search%20is%20on%20for%20co-accused%20Ravindra%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714018920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5iq18e4g_faridabad-bank-manager_625x300_25_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fkidnapping-at-gunpoint-then-800-km-drive-faridabad-bank-manager-rescued-5518059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bank%20manager%2C%20who%20was%20kidnapped%20at%20gunpoint%20Saturday%20from%20his%20Faridabad%20home%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh's%20Bilaspur%20and%20then%20Mathura%2C%20has%20been%20rescued%2C%20thanks%20to%20swift%20action%20by%20Haryana%20police's%20crime%20branch%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fkidnapping-at-gunpoint-then-800-km-drive-faridabad-bank-manager-rescued-5518059%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fkidnapping-at-gunpoint-then-800-km-drive-faridabad-bank-manager-rescued-5518059%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fkidnapping-at-gunpoint-then-800-km-drive-faridabad-bank-manager-rescued-5518059%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20reports%20Chinese%20military%20incursions%20near%20island%20amid%20escalating%20tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714018880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109580753%2Cimgsize-296042.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-reports-chinese-military-incursions-near-island-amid-escalating-tensions%2Farticleshow%2F109580691.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109580691.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22ca