rnment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shekhawat%20had%20filed%20a%20police%20case%20accusing%20Lokesh%20Sharma%20of%20leaking%20the%20alleged%20conversation.%20He%20also%20filed%20a%20defamation%20case%20against%20Mr%20Gehlot%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20tapping%20case%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Crime%20Branch%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20who%20had%20summoned%20Lokesh%20Sharma%20earlier%20for%20questioning.%20He%20is%20currently%20on%20bail%20from%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20ordered%20non-coercive%20action%20against%20him%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELokesh%20Sharma%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20close%20aides%20were%20protected%20by%20him%20in%20the%20REET%20paper%20leak%20issue%20of%202022.%20The%20leaking%20of%20the%20teachers'%20training%20exam%20paper%20or%20REET%20was%20also%20a%20political%20issue%20raised%20by%20the%20state's%20Opposition%20BJP%20in%20last%20year's%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20has%20recently%20been%20tweeting%20against%20his%20former%20boss%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20he%20has%20openly%20spoken%20out%20about%20allegations%20of%20phone%20tapping%20---%C2%A0%20his%20disclosures%20timed%20just%20a%20day%20ahead%20of%20voting%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20especially%20voting%20in%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20constituency%20Jodhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gehlot%2C%20who%20is%20in%20Jodhpur%20after%20campaigning%2C%20has%20so%20far%20not%20commented%20on%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714018080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F36ptqv48_ashok-gehlot-lokesh-sharma_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-eve-of-phase-2-polls-phone-tapping-allegations-again-against-ashok-gehlot-5516704%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Rajasthan%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20former%20aide%20Lokesh%20Sharma%20has%20