th%20an%20excruciating%20rare%20medical%20condition%20which%20leaves%20her%20permanently%20aroused.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Scarlet%20Kaitlin%20Wallen%20has%20persistent%20genital%20arousal%20disorder%20(PGAD)%2C%20a%20condition%20which%20causes%20uncontrollable%20arousal.%20She%20was%20just%20six%20when%20she%20began%20to%20feel%20severe%20and%20constant%20%26quot%3Bpins-and-needles%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20genitals.%20She%20said%20that%20ever%20since%20her%20symptoms%20started%20showing%20she's%20only%20had%20a%20handful%20of%20painful%20days%2C%20which%20has%20left%20her%20unable%20to%20work%20or%20study%20full-time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPGAD%20affects%20one%20per%20of%20the%20population%2C%20even%20though%20not%20everyone's%20symptoms%20are%20very%20severe.%20For%20Ms%20Wallen%2C%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20has%20been%20just%20marred%20with%20excruciating%20pain.%20As%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F23%2Flifestyle%2Frare-medical-condition-makes-me-permanently-aroused-and-its-ruined-my-life%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2021-year-old%20has%20even%20had%20some%20of%20her%20genital%20nerves%20removed%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20numb%20the%20pain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20been%20experiencing%20pain%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20remember.%20My%20vulva%20was%20constantly%20burning%20-%20it%20was%20like%20I%20was%20naturally%20aroused%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20it.%20There's%20nerve%20pain%2C%20it's%20not%20wanted%20-%20and%20there's%20no%20pleasure.%20I'm%20hopeful%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20have%20a%20painless%20sexual%20relationship%20in%20my%20lifetime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Wallen%20said%20when%20her%20PGAD%20started%20at%206%2C%20it%20stopped%20her%20from%20playing%20with%20her%20friends.%20She%20described%20the%20pain%20as%20%26quot%3Bburning%20bugs%20under%20my%20skin%26quot%3B%20and%20like%20her%20genitals%20were%20on%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20Ms%20Wallen%20said%20she%20started%20experiencing%20random%20days%20without%20pain.%20But%20the%20burning%20and%20unwanted%20arousal%20would%20come%20back%20with%20a%20vengeance%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20she%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmysterious-liquid-trickle-from-spirit-airlines-bathroom-horrifying-passengers-5517679%5C%22%3EMysterious%20Liquid%20Trickle%20From%20Spirit%20Airlines'%20Bathroom%2C%20Horrifying%20Passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2021-year-old%20said%20she%20would%20deliberately%20use%20vapour%20rub%20on%20her%20genitals%20to%20distract%20from%20the%20unwanted%20arousal.%20Chemicals%20in%20the%20rub%20would%20give%20her%20severe%20thrush%20but%20she%20found%20the%20%26quot%3Brawness%20and%20burning%26quot%3B%20more%20tolerable%20than%20the%20pain%20from%20PGAD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20graduating%20from%20high%20school%2C%20Ms%20Wallen%20saw%20a%20doctor.%20Her%20clinician%20was%20certain%20that%20she%20was%20suffering%20from%20PGAD%20alongside%20her%20other%20sexual%20dysfunctions.%20The%20doctor%20also%20found%20she%20was%20suffering%20from%20congenital%20neuroproliferative%20vestibulodynia%2C%20which%20means%20the%20pelvic%20nerves%20are%20hypersensitive%20to%20touch%2C%20and%20Ms%20Wallen%20has%20been%20suffering%20from%20this%20since%20birth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Wallen%20then%20had%20genital%20nerves%20removed%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20numb%20the%20pain%20but%20she%20only%20had%20parts%20of%20the%20painful%20tissue%20removed%2C%20giving%20her%20a%20greater%20chance%20of%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20sex%20drive%20in%20the%20future.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20treatments%20and%20surgeries%20being%20developed%20all%20the%20time%2C%20Ms%20Wallen%20remains%20hopeful%20she'll%