.com%2Fphoto%2F109578541.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20Lara%20Dutta%20who%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20her%20upcoming%20drama%20series%20'Ranneeti%3A%20Balakot%20%26amp%3B%20Beyond'%2C%20is%20spilling%20the%20beans%20about%20dealing%20with%20online%20trolling%20and%20negativity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JEE%20Main%202024%20Results%20Declared%2C%2056%20Candidates%20Score%20100%20Percentile%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20released%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Joint%20Entrance%20Examination%20(JEE)%20Main%202024%20for%20Paper%201%20(BE%2FBTech)%20of%20the%20January%20and%20April%20sessions%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20A%20total%20of%2056%20examinees%20aced%20the%20engineering%20entrance%20exam%20with%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20100%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20hailing%20from%20Telangana.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20JEE%20Main%202024%20exams%20were%20conducted%20in%20two%20sessions%20-%20the%20first%20session%20took%20place%20on%20January%2028%2C%2029%2C%2030%2C%2031%2C%20and%20February%2001%2C%20while%20the%20second%20session%20on%20April%204%2C%205%2C%206%2C%208%2C%20and%209.%C2%A0The%20examinations%20were%20conducted%20in%20computer-based%20Test%20(CBT)%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2010%2C67%2C95%20students%20took%20the%20second%20session%20of%20Paper%201%20(BE%2FBTech)%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20who%20achieved%20a%20perfect%20score%2C%2015%20are%20from%20Telangana%2C%20with%20seven%20each%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20six%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjeemain.nta.ac.in%2Fimages%2Fpress-release-for-the-release-of-rank-and-nta-scores-for-jee-main-2024-session-2-dated-24-april-2024.pdf%5C%22%3ECheck%20the%20merit%20list%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThirty-nine%20candidates%20were%20barred%20from%20future%20attempts%20for%20three%20years%20due%20to%20engaging%20in%20malpractice%20during%20the%20examination%2C%20the%20NTA%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20examinations%20were%20held%20in%2013%20languages%20-%20Assamese%2C%20Bengali%2C%20English%2C%20Gujarati%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Kannada%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Marathi%2C%20Odia%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%2C%20and%20Urdu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20session%20of%20the%20JEE%20(Main)%202024%20took%20place%20across%20571%20examination%20centres%20spanning%20319%20cities%2C%20with%2022%20centres%20located%20overseas.%20The%20first%20session%20was%20held%20in%20approximately%20544%20centres%20across%20291%20cities%2C%20including%2021%20centres%20outside%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20required%20JEE%20(Main)%20percentile%20for%20qualification%20to%20the%20JEE%20(Advanced)%20has%20reached%20its%20highest%20point%20in%20five%20years%20across%20all%20categories.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20minimum%20cutoff%20for%20the%20general%20category%20stands%20at%2093.2%2C%20showing%20an%20increase%20from%2090.7%20in%202023%20and%2088.4%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20policy%2C%20the%20NTA%20doesn't%20disclose%20raw%20scores%20but%20instead%20provides%20percentiles.%20The%20percentile%20score%2C%20which%20is%20a%20normalised%20score%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20is%20used%20in%20compiling%20merit%20lists%20rather%20than%20the%20candidate's%20raw%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714013760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fadlo41m8_jee-mains_625x300_17_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fjee-main-2024-results-declared-56-candidates-score-100-percentile-5517645%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JEE%20Main%202024%20Results%3A%20Of%20the%20students%20who%20attained%20a%20perfect%20score%2C%2015%20are%20from%20Telangana%2C%20seven%20each%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%2