0%20WC%20squad%20by%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20is%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20leading%20scorer%20this%20season%20with%20303%20runs%20in%20eight%20games.%20He's%20scored%20almost%204000%20runs%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is%20and%20will%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20powerplay%20overs%20as%20India's%20opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20slow%20start%20to%20IPL%202024%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20finally%20found%20form%20when%20he%20scored%20an%20unbeaten%20104%20against%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20Rajasthan%20Royals'%20last%20encounter.%20Jaiswal%20has%20managed%20225%20runs%20in%20eight%20games%20for%20the%20Royals%20this%20season%20and%20boasts%20four%20fifties%20as%20well%20as%20a%20ton%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20161.93%20in%20T20Is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShubman%20Gill%20hasn't%20set%20the%20T20I%20stage%20ablaze%20despite%20scoring%20a%20hundred%20and%20fifty%20for%20India.%20His%20form%20as%20Gujarat%20Titans'%20skipper%20in%20IPL%202024%20though%20puts%20him%20in%20the%20reckoning.%20He%20has%20made%20298%20runs%20in%20eight%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2042.57%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20146.97%20in%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20IPL%202024%20with%20379%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2063.16%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20150.39%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20a%20certainty%20for%20India's%20squad.%20He's%20made%20the%20most%20runs%20(4037)%20in%20T20Is%20with%20an%20average%20of%20over%2050%2C%20making%20his%20inclusion%20in%20the%20squad%20a%20no-brainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanju%20Samson%20(WK)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20impressive%20wicketkeeper%20batter%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20Rajasthan%20Royals'%20skipper%20Sanju%20Samson%20has%20made%20314%20runs%20in%20eight%20games%20at%20an%20average%20of%2062.80%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20152.42%20in%20the%20ongoing%20season.%20He%20hasn't%20shown%20his%20best%20for%20India%20in%20T20Is%20but%20is%20capable%20of%20wreaking%20havoc%20with%20the%20bat%20if%20given%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20sidelined%20for%20the%20first%20few%20games%20of%20IPL%202024%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20has%20still%20managed%20to%20impress%20courtesy%20of%20140%20runs%20in%20five%20games%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20166.66.%20The%20world's%20No.1%20T20I%20batter%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20has%20made%20more%20than%202000%20T20I%20runs%2C%20including%20four%20centuries%20and%2017%20fifties%20at%20an%20average%20of%2045.55%20and%20strike%20rate%20of%20171.55.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardik%20Pandya%20hasn't%20enjoyed%20his%20return%20to%20Mumbai%20Indians%20as%20skipper%20in%20IPL%202024%20having%20struggled%20with%20both%20bat%20and%20ball.%20He's%20managed%20151%20runs%20as%20well%20as%20four%20wickets%20in%20IPL%202024%20but%20is%20likely%20to%20sneak%20into%20the%20squad%20considering%20his%20abundance%20of%20experience%20in%20T20Is%2C%20where%20he's%20scored%201348%20runs%20and%20taken%2073%20scalps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERishabh%20Pant%20(WK)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20away%20from%20the%20game%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20due%20to%20a%20serious%20car%20crash%2C%20wicketkeeper%20batter%20Rishabh%20Pant%20has%20made%20a%20strong%20comeback%20in%20IPL%202024.%20He's%20scored%20254%20runs%20in%20eight%20games%20and%20has%20gone%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20150.29%2C%20making%20him%20a%20worthy%20contender%20for%20India's%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20belligerent%20finisher%20who%20doesn't%20take%20much%20time%20to%20get%20his%20eye%20in%2