0of%20the%20bird%20flu%20virus%20in%20pasteurised%20cow%20milk%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20sparked%20questions%20over%20whether%20the%20disease%20could%20spread%20to%20humans%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20there%20is%20little%20risk%20from%20food%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20authorities%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20they%20had%20discovered%20traces%20of%20bird%20flu%20virus%20in%20the%20cow%20milk%20supply%20during%20the%20course%20of%20a%20large%20study%2C%20but%20the%20samples%20likely%20posed%20no%20health%20risk%20to%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20outbreak%20of%20Highly%20Pathogenic%20Avian%20Influenza%20(HPAI)%20has%20spread%20among%20dairy%20cattle%20herds%20throughout%20the%20United%20States%20and%20infected%20one%20human%2C%20who%20had%20mild%20symptoms%2C%20authorities%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20H5N1%20strain%20of%20HPAI%20has%20killed%20millions%20of%20poultry%20during%20the%20current%20wave%2C%20affected%20cows%20have%20not%20fallen%20severely%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20said%20that%20during%20the%20course%20of%20a%20national%20survey%2C%20it%20had%20discovered%20viral%20particles%20in%20%26quot%3Bmilk%20from%20affected%20animals%2C%20in%20the%20processing%20system%2C%20and%20on%20the%20shelves%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20samples%20were%20run%20through%20a%20quantitative%20polymerase%20chain%20reaction%20(qPCR)%20test%2C%20which%20is%20able%20to%20detect%20remnants%20of%20the%20pathogen's%20genetic%20material%20--%20though%20the%20virus%20itself%20was%20inactivated%20by%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20pasteurisation%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20it%20happen%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bird%20flu%20A%2FH5N1%20strain%20first%20appeared%20in%201996%20but%20since%202020%20the%20number%20of%20contaminated%20bird%20populations%20has%20exploded%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20mammals%20have%20since%20been%20infected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20both%20cows%20and%20goats%20joined%20the%20list%2C%20a%20surprise%20for%20experts%20because%20until%20now%20the%20animals%20had%20not%20been%20considered%20at%20risk%20of%20catching%20this%20type%20of%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20a%20new%20H5N1%20virus%20has%20intermingled%20with%20local%20viruses%2C%20and%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20multiply%20extremely%20rapidly%20in%20a%20cow's%20udder%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jean-Claude%20Manuguerra%2C%20director%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20infection%20risks%20department%20at%20the%20Pasteur%20Institute%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20H5N1%20has%20killed%20millions%20of%20poultry%20during%20the%20current%20wave%2C%20infected%20cows%20have%20not%20become%20seriously%20ill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPandemic%20risk%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20studies%20to%20date%2C%20most%20experts%20say%20that%20even%20if%20the%20bird%20flu%20virus%20spreads%20to%20a%20human%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20widespread%20contamination%20are%20slim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20fact%20that%20virus%20traces%20have%20been%20found%20in%20cow%20milk%20worrying%3F%20No%2C%20although%20the%20fact%20that%20another%20animal%20is%20susceptible%20to%20contamination%20by%20this%20virus%20is%20not%20good%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bruno%20Lina%2C%20a%20virologist%20at%20the%20Lyon%20hospital%20in%20southeast%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20risk%20of%20random%20cases%2C%20in%20animals%20or%20humans.%20But%20we're%20not%20seeing%20any%20major%20mutation%20of%20the%20virus%20that%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20greater%20pandemic%20risk%20than%20three%20or%20four%20months%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20health%20threat%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20authorities%20said%20earlier%20in%20April%20that%20a%20person%20working%20on%20a%20dairy%20farm%20in%20Texas%20was%20recovering%20from%20bird%20flu%20after%20being%20exposed%20to%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symptoms%20were%20mild%2C%20with%20only%20an%20eye%20infection%2C%20after%20being%20in%20direct%20contact%20with%20a%20cow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20know%20is%20that%20the%20virus%20can%20cause%20in%20humans%20an%20infection%20in%20two%20specific%20places%3A%20an%20eye%20infection%20--%20which%20is%20mild%20--%20or%20in%20the%20pulmonary%20alveoli%2C%20the%20deepest%20parts%20of%20the%20lung%2C%26quot%3B%20Lina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latter%20case%2C%20the%20infection%20can%20prove%20serious%20--%20of%20the%20roughly%20900%20cases%20of%20H5N1%20documented%20in%20humans%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20half%20have%20ended%20in%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20drinking%20pasteurised%20milk%2C%20the%20risks%20drop%20to%20nearly%20zero%20even%20if%20virus%20traces%20are%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPasteurisation%20destroys%20the%20virus%20even%20if%20it%20doesn't%20eradicate%20every%20trace%20of%20its%20presence%2C%26quot%3B%20Lina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20raw%20milk%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20countries%20such%20as%20France%20are%20fond%20of%20their%20raw%20chesses%2C%20but%20experts%20note%20that%20the%20sanitary%20conditions%20of%20their%20production%20are%20strictly%20controlled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHas%20anyone%20ever%20been%20exposed%20to%20non-pasteurised%20milk%20contaminated%20by%20H5N1%2C%20and%20developed%20an%20infection%20by%20the%20normal%20means%20of%20consumption%2C%20the%20mouth%20or%20digestive%20tract%3F%20It's%20never%20been%20demonstrated%2C%26quot%3B%20Lina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20now%2C%20the%20latest%20virus%20strain%20discovered%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%20different%20from%20those%20currently%20circulating%20in%20Europe%2C%20said%20Manuguerra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%20H5N1%20infections%20have%20so%20far%20been%20found%20in%20French%20cows%2C%20for%20example%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20warning%20has%20been%20sounded%2C%20there%20is%20extra%20vigilance%20--%20and%20these%20viruses%20can%20mutate%20so%20rapidly%20that%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20that%20consumers%20should%20absolutely%20not%20be%20worried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714012980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Flje541h8_cow-generic_625x300_25_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fbird-flu-virus-found-in-cow-milk-supply-will-it-impact-humans-5517640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20discovery%20of%20traces%20of%20the%20bird%20flu%20virus%20in%20pasteurised%20cow%20milk%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20sparked%20questions%20over%20whether%20the%20disease%20could%20spread%20to%20humans%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20there%20is%20little%20risk%20from%20food%20contamination.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fbird-flu-virus-found-in-cow-milk-supply-will-it-impact-humans-5517640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fbird-flu-virus-found-in-cow-milk-supply-will-it-impact-humans-5517640%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhealth%2Fbird-flu-virus-found-in-cow-milk-supply-will-it-impact-humans-5517640%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kriti%20blushes%20as%20photographers%20call%20her%20'Vahini'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2