ed%20stratospheric%20heights%20in%20cricket%20in%20national%20colours%20while%20also%20plying%20his%20trade%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%2C%20shared%20memories%20from%20the%20time%20when%20he%20was%20signed%20on%20to%20feature%20for%20the%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20by%20former%20owner%20Vijay%20Mallya%20in%20the%202008%20auction.%20In%20the%20inaugural%20IPL%20auction%2C%20Kumble%20went%20under%20the%20hammer%20after%20he%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20initial%20list%20of%20icon%20players.%20Batting%20talisman%20and%20present%20India%20head%20coach%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20featured%20in%20the%20list%20of%20the%20RCB's%20icon%20players%2C%20ahead%20of%20Kumble%2C%20who%20was%20nicknamed%20'Jumbo'%20during%20his%20playing%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumble%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20scalping%20all%20ten%20wickets%20in%20a%20single%20innings%20in%20Test%20cricket%20alongside%20England's%20Jim%20Laker%20and%20New%20Zealand's%20Ejaz%20Patel%2C%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20RCB%20at%20his%20base%20price%20after%20Mallya%20insisted%20at%20the%20auction%20that%20'nobody'%20was%20to%20touch%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20my%20Bangalore%20boy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%20I%20mean%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20I%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20India%20in%20the%20Test%20and%20for%20some%20reason%20I%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20icon%20list%20so%20I%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20auction.%20Which%20I%20obviously%20didn't%20participate%20in%20but%20my%20name%20was%20in%20the%20auction%20list.%20I%20remember%20somebody%20telling%20me%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20my%20name%20came%20up%20it%20is%20not%20how%20it%20is%20like%20now%20when%20my%20name%20came%20up%20Mr%20Vijay%20Mallya%20just%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20he's%20my%20Bangalore%20boy.%20Nobody%20is%20touching%20him%20and%20that%20was%20the%20end%20of%20any%20other%20bid%20coming.%20I%20think%20that%20was%20the%20base%20price%20that%20I%20was%20bought%20at%20and%20there%20was%20no%20auction%20dynamics%20that%20you%20see%20today.%20So%20that%20was%20what%20I%20was%20told%20there%20were%20no%20(other%20buyers)%20because%20the%20owner%20just%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20no%20way%2C%20no%20way%20he%20is%20going%20anywhere%20else%20other%20than%20Bangalore%2C%26quot%3B%20Kumble%20said%20during%20a%20heart-to-heart%20chat%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20latter's%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20three-year%20stint%20with%20RCB%2C%20Kumble%20made%2042%20appearances%20for%20the%20Bengaluru%20franchise%2C%20picking%20up%2045%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2023.51%20and%20an%20economy%20of%206.58.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20better%20part%20of%20his%20career%2C%20Kumble%20predominantly%20featured%20in%20Test%20and%20ODI%20formats%2C%20as%20T20Is%20came%20into%20the%20cricketing%20currency%20during%20the%20latter%20stages%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20challenges%20he%20faced%20in%20changing%20his%20approach%20from%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20cricket%20to%20the%20shortest%20format%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20inaugural%20IPL%20season%2C%20Kumble%20recalled%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20quite%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20my%20mind%20around%20to%20bowl%20just%20four%20overs%20because%20the%20time%20that%20I%20started%20playing%20I%20needed%20four%20overs%20to%20warm%20up.%20The%20body%20required%20that%20kind%20of%20overs%20to%20bowl%2055%20to%2060%20overs%20in%20a%20Test%20match%20on%20an%20average%20and%20to%20come%20back%20to%20think%20that%20if%20you%20end%20up%20bowling%2060%20overs%20you%20would%20be%20done%20with%20the%20tournament.%20It%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20me%20to%20change%20that%20mindset.%20But%20it%20became%20very%20evident%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20approach%20my%20four%20overs%20would%20be%20try%20and%20choose%20the%20most%20challenging%20ones.%20That's%20how%20you%20probably%20get%20more%20into%20the%20game%20rather%20than%20just%20thinking%20that%20bowl%20four%20overs%2C%20end%20your%20spell%20and%20then%20wait%20for%20the%20batters%20to%20do%20their%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20cash-rich%20domestic%20league%2C%20the%20RCB%20made%20it%20to%20the%20final%20but%20fell%20at%20the%20final%20hurdle%20against%20the%20Deccan%20Chargers%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20franchise%20that%20no%20longer%20features%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714010820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F%2Fvijay-mallya-afp_625x300_1530006632687.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fvijay-mallya-said-nobody-is-touching-india-great-reveals-his-ipl-bid-tale-5515462%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20player%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20RCB%20at%20his%20base%20price%20after%20Vijay%20Mallya%20insisted%20at%20the%20auction%20that%20'nobody'%20was%20to%20touch%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bhe's%20my%20Bangalore%20boy%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamaearth%20parent%20bets%20on%20Made-for-India%20goods%20in%20fastest-growing%20beauty%20mkt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714010331000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F25%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1714009751-5552.jp