%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Burnham%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Eastman%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20phenomenon%20of%20partisan%20lawfare%20grows%20more%20troubling%20by%20the%20day.%20%C2%A0Professor%20Eastman%20is%20innocent%20of%20criminal%20conduct%20in%20Arizona%20or%20any%20other%20place%20and%20will%20fight%20these%20charges%20as%20he%20has%20all%20the%20other%20unjust%20accusations%20leveled%20against%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Terwilliger%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Meadows%2C%20told%20the%20Post%20he%20hadn't%20seen%20the%20indictment%20but%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Mr.%20Meadows%20is%20named%20in%20this%20indictment%2C%20it%20is%20a%20blatantly%20political%20and%20politicized%20accusation%20and%20will%20be%20contested%20and%20defeated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20referred%20to%20%26quot%3BUnindicted%20Coconspirator%201%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20is%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20former%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20who%20spread%20false%20claims%20of%20election%20fraud%20following%20the%202020%20election.%26quot%3B%20Another%20four%20people%20who%20are%20not%20named%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20unindicted%20coconspirators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArizona%20was%20one%20of%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Georgia%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Nevada%2C%20in%20which%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fake-electors-2020-gop-biden-electoral-votes-certification-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efake%20electors%3C%2Fa%3E%20tried%20to%20cast%20electoral%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Evotes%20for%20Trump%20despite%20Joe%20Biden%20winning%20the%20election%20in%20their%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Arizona%20attorney%20general's%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for