llc-small-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20wearing%20aprons%20smile%20while%20looking%20at%20phone%20in%20front%20of%20a%20storefront.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6604819f16bde8d4ead2d353%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20LLC%20can%20protect%20your%20assets%20from%20your%20company's%20liabilities.%3Cp%3EKentaroo%20Tryman%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20exact%20steps%20for%20forming%20an%20LLC%20vary%20by%20state%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20similar%20process%20in%20most%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou'll%20need%20a%20business%20name%2C%20a%20registered%20agent%2C%20articles%20of%20organization%2C%20and%20an%20operating%20agreement%20in%20certain%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ESave%20%2425%20when%20using%20Block%20Advisors%20to%20form%20your%20LLC%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Discount%20applied%20in%20cart.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20working%20on%20setting%20up%20your%20own%20business%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20you're%20looking%20to%20open%20a%20limited%20liability%20company%2C%20or%20LLC.%20This%20business%20structure%20gives%20you%20limited%20liability%20protection%20similar%20to%20a%20corporation%2C%20plus%20the%20flexibility%20of%20a%20sole%20proprietorship%20or%20partnership%2C%20making%20it%20a%20popular%20choice%20for%20small%20business%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20perk%20of%20an%20LLC%20is%20that%20it%20generally%20can%20protect%20your%20personal%20assets%20(like%20the%20money%20you're%20saving%20up%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20or%20retire)%20from%20certain%20liabilities%20or%20debt%20that%20come%20with%20owning%20your%20business.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20a%20creditor%20you%20owe%20money%20to%20through%20your%20business%20usually%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20come%20for%20the%20money%20in%20your%20personal%20accounts.%20Having%20an%20LLC%20can%20also%20legitimize%20your%20business%2C%20which%20may%20be%20a%20benefit%20to%20many%20small%20business%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20sounds%20good%2C%20follow%20these%20steps%20to%20open%20your%20LLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Check%20what%20requirements%20your%20state%20has%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELLCs%20are%20regulated%20by%20states%2C%20which%20means%20that%20you'll%20have%20to%20meet%20the%20specific%20requirements%20outlined%20by%20the%20state%20where%20you're%20registering%20the%20LLC.%20You'll%20find%20this%20information%20easily%20on%20your%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20steps%20necessary%20to%20establish%20an%20LLC%20will%20need%20to%20be%20done%20no%20matter%20which%20state%20you%20live%20in%2C%20the%20specific%20guidance%20for%20how%20to%20do%20each%20step%20%E2%80%94%20like%20naming%20your%20business%20and%20picking%20a%20registered%20agent%20%E2%80%94%20can%20vary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Name%20your%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20you%20have%20a%20business%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20choose%20a%20name%20for%20it.%20While%20you'll%20want%20something%20catchy%20and%20easy%20to%20market%2C%20it's%20also%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20name%20you%20choose%20meets%20your%20specific%20state's%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20name%20you%20choose%20isn't%20being%20used%20by%20another%20LLC%20in%20your%20state.%20You%20can%20typically%20do%20a%20name%20search%20on%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20website%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.ilsos.gov%2Fbusinessentitysearch%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20Illinois'%20search%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20have%20certain%20words%20in%20the%20name%20that%20make%20it%20clear%20your%20business%20is%20an%20LLC%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BLimited%20Liability%20Company%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLLC%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BL.L.C.%26quot%3B%20Many%20states%20will%20also%20prohibit%20you%20from%20including%20certain%20words%20in%20the%20name.%20In%20New%20York%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20you%20can't%20include%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bacademy%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bbank%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bfinance%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bunion%26quot%3B%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdos.ny.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2F2018%2F10%2Frestrictedwordsphrases.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20many%20more%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Pick%20a%20registered%20agent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20LLC%20has%20to%20have%20a%20registered%20agent%20who%20acts%20as%20the%20point%20person%20for%20any%20legal%20matters%20that%20may%20come%20up%20and%20for%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20to%20send%20any%20official%20paperwork%20to.%20Generally%2C%20that%20person%20(or%20business)%20must%20have%20a%20physical%20address%20in%20the%20state%20where%20your%20LLC%20is%20registered%20and%20be%20available%20to%20receive%20mail%20there%20during%20working%20hours.%20They%20also%20have%20to%20be%20at%20least%2018%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20name%20yourself%20as%20the%20registered%20agent%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20the%20best%20idea.%20If%20you're%20worried%20you%20might%20not%20be%20available%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20point%20person%20or%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20important%20mail%2C%20it%20might%20be%20best%20to%20outsource%20this%20role.%20There%20are%20registered%20agent%20services%20you%20can%20use%2C%20though%20they'll%20come%20at%20a%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20File%20your%20articles%20of%20organization%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20head%20back%20to%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State's%20website%20to%20find%20the%20articles%20of%20organization%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20file.%20You%20can%20also%20meet%20with%20someone%20in%20the%20department%20in%20person%20or%20by%20phone%20if%20you%20prefer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20information%20you'll%20have%20to%20fill%20out%20for%20the%20articles%20of%20organization%20will%20vary%20by%20state.%20Still%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20be%20asked%20for%20basic%20information%20like%20your%20LLC's%20name%2C%20address%2C%20services%2C%20and%20how%20you%20expect%20it%20to%20be%20managed.%20You'll%20also%20need%20to%20pay%20a%20filing%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20articles%20of%20an%20organization%20may%20be%20called%20something%20different%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20state.%20Alabama%20and%20Texas%2C%20for%20example%2C%20call%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bcertificate%20of%20formation.%26quot%3B%20Some%20states%20also%20have%20publication%20requirements%2C%20which%20means%20you%20need%20to%20publish%20an%20announcement%20of%20your%20new%20business%20in%20a%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Create%20an%20operating%20agreement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you'll%20likely%20divvy%20up%20responsibilities%20for%20anyone%20in%20your%20business%20on%20your%20own%2C%20you%20may%20also%20be%20required%20to%20do%20so%20via%20an%20operating%20agreement.%20These%20agreements%20outline%20how%20your%20business%20will%20be%20run%20and%20delegate%20roles%20and%20power%20to%20different%20members.%20That%20may%20include%20voting%20procedures%2C%20rules%20around%20daily%20operations%2C%20and%20ownership%20rights%20within%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20some%20states%20require%20you%20to%20create%20this%20type%20of%20agreement%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20do%20so%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20technically%20have%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E6.%20Take%20care%20of%20other%20business%20tasks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpening%20an%20LLC%20may%20be%20your%20first%20priority%2C%20but%20there%20are%20other%20tasks%20to%20take%20care%20of%20during%20the%20process%2C%20like%20getting%20your%20employer%20identification%20number%20(EIN).%20An%20EIN%20is%20an%20identifying%20number%20that%20the%20IRS%20will%20use%20for%20tax%20reasons%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20always%20required%20for%20opening%20an%20LLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20want%20to%20open%20a%20business%20bank%20account%20to%20ensure%20you%20keep%20your%20personal%20and%20business%20assets%20separate%20for%20bookkeeping%20and%20tax%20purposes.%20Plus%2C%20look%20into%20what%20exactly%20you%20need%20to%20keep%20your%20LLC%20active%20in%20your%20state%2C%20which%20may%20include%20filing%20an%20annual%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E7.%20Consider%20using%20a%20professional%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20goes%20into%20opening%20and%20operating%20your%20own%20business%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20take%20care%20of%20everything%20on%20your%20own.%3Cspan%3E%20Block%20Advisors%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20part%20of%20H%26amp%3BR%20Block%2C%20can%20help%20you%20decide%20which%20type%20of%20business%20structure%20is%20best%20for%20you%2C%20such%20as%20an%20LLC%2C%20and%20help%20you%20open%20that%20business.%20Using%20an%20online%20service%20to%20incorporate%20your%20business%20will%20help%20ensure%20that%20you%20submit%20all%20of%20the%20necessary%20paperwork%20required%20in%20your%20state%20of%20incorporation.%20This%20could%20save%20you%20time%20now%20and%20headaches%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Block%20Advisors%2C%20you're%20not%20on%20your%20own%20once%20your%20business%20is%20up%20and%20running.%20The%20service%20provides%20tax%20help%2C%20including%20filing%20your%20taxes%20with%20a%20professional%20or%20on%20your%20own%20with%20help%20from%20a%20live%20expert.%20You%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20one%20of%20its%3Cspan%3E%20bookkeeping%20services%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20which%20range%20from%20a%20step-by-step%20guide%20to%20doing%20your%20own%20bookkeeping%20to%20working%20with%20your%20own%20dedicated%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20scale%2C%20Block%20Advisors%20also%20offers%20payroll%20services%2C%20which%20help%20you%20pay%20your%20employees%20each%20pay%20cycle%20and%20can%20make%20sure%20you%20stay%20compliant.%20There%20are%20three%20tiers%20to%20choose%20from%20%E2%80%94%20the%20basic%20service%20comes%20with%20a%20dedicated%20accountant%2C%20up%20to%20the%20premium%20service%2C%20which%20includes%20timekeeping%2C%20human%20resources%20assistance%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERegister%20your%20LLC%20with%20Block%20Advisors%20today%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20you%20can%20save%20%2425%20(discount%20applied%20in%20cart).%20New%20bookkeeping%20clients%20can%20also%20get%20a%20month%20free%20when%20referencing%20code%20BKFREE%20during%20a%20bookkeeping%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*This%20article%20is%20for%20informational%20purposes%20only%20and%20should%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20legal%20advice.%20You%20may%20want%20to%20seek%20the%20advice%20of%20an%20attorney%20to%20evaluate%20all%20relevant%20considerations%20in%20forming%20a%20business%20entity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E**Block%20Advisors%20discount%20may%20not%20be%20combined%20with%20any%20other%20offer%20or%20promotion.%20Void%20if%20transferred%20and%20where%20prohibited.%20Discount%20will%20appear%20in%20your%20cart%20automatically%20when%20you%20use%20the%20link.%20No%20cash%20value.%20Expires%20June%2030%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsteps-start-llc-small-business%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713995319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660481923f923f7dab01dedd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsteps-start-llc-small-business%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20starting%20a%20small%20business%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20your%20personal%20assets%20are%20protected%20from%20your%20business%20liabilities%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20an%20LLC%20does.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsteps-start-llc-small-business%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Matty%20Healy%20Hasn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98Really%20Listened%20to%20Much%E2%80%99%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Tortured%20Poets%E2%80%99%20Album%2C%20%E2%80%98but%20I%E2%80%99m%20Sure%20It%E2%80%99s%20Good%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713993403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGettyImages-1694098084-e1696953236932.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235981215%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%201975%E2%80%99s%20Matty%20Healy%20has%20weighed%20in%20%E2%80%94%20sort%20of%20%E2%80%94%20on%20Taylor%20Swift%E2%80%99s%20new%20album%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Tortured%20Poets%20Department%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20many%20speculated%20includes%20songs%20that%20are%20written%20about%20the%20singer.%20In%20a%20brief%20on-the-street%20inter