%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20participated%20in%20several%20challenges%2C%20but%20crossing%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20is%20one%20for%20the%20country.%20While%20we%20were%20swimming%20the%20stretch%2C%20we%20were%20filled%20with%20mixed%20emotions%2C%20of%20celebrating%20the%20spirit%20of%20universal%20brotherhood%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20calling%20out%20to%20the%20nation%20to%20nurture%20swimming%20as%20a%20key%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shaaswat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20greeted%20by%20hundreds%20of%20young%20boys%20and%20girls%20at%20Dhanushkodi%2C%20making%20it%20all%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20all%20boils%20down%20to%20proper%20planning%20and%20collaboration.%20If%20you%20dream%20and%20put%20in%20the%20effort%2C%20there%20are%20people%20to%20support%20you.%20Dream%20big%2C%20follow%20your%20passion%2C%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20hesitate%20to%20extend%20your%20voice%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20We%20need%20more%20youngsters%20getting%20into%20swimming%20as%20a%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713873383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D348050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bharat%20Sachdeva%20and%20Shaaswat%20Sharma%20swam%20non-stop%20across%20the%20challenging%2032%20km%20stretch%20near%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20in%2010%20hours%2030%20minutes.%20Their%20aim%3F%20To%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20swimming%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348050%2Fbharat-sachdeva-shaaswat-sharma-swimmers-palk-strait-ram-setu-india-sri-lanka-open-water-swimming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%