hild%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99%20as%20well%2C%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAppetite%20is%20a%20natural%20phenomenon.%20The%20idea%20of%20getting%20the%20child%20to%20eat%20the%20same%20as%20the%20family%20is%20to%20prevent%20fussy%20eaters.%20They%20should%20get%20used%20to%20everything%20one%20eats%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20baby%20is%20a%20clean%20slate%2C%20and%20will%20accept%20anything%20you%20give.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20I%20started%20cow%E2%80%99s%20milk%20for%20my%20son%20after%20he%20turned%20one%2C%20I%20did%20not%20add%20any%20sugar%20or%20sweetener%20to%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20just%20boiled%20and%20cooled%2C%20and%20he%20loves%20it%2C%20since%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20other%20taste.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarima%20Dev%20Verman%2C%20a%20certified%20nutritionist%20and%20medical%20content%20analyst%20with%20The%20Healthy%20Indian%20Project%20(THIP)%2C%20states%20that%20if%20we%20start%20a%20baby%20on%20the%20sweetened%2C%20powdered%20baby%20food%20at%20six%20months%2C%20he%20or%20she%20won%E2%80%99t%20accept%20anything%20else%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20sugar%20in%20one%20serving%20of%20Cerelac%20is%20too%20much%2C%20which%20is%20not%20at%20all%20required%20by%20a%20baby.%20Sugar%20is%20addictive%2C%20leading%20to%20babies%20demanding%20only%20sweet%20foods%20then.%20You%20can%20instead%20use%20fruits%20which%20are%20naturally%20sweet%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20the%20important%20nutrients%20that%20a%20baby%20needs%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20baby%20needs%20a%20balanced%20diet%2C%20comprising%20all%20essential%20nutrients.%20Every%20meal%20for%20a%20baby%20must%20include%20fats%2C%20carbohydrates%20and%20protein%2C%20says%20Sanchita%20Daswani%2C%20a%20nutrition%20consultant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIron%20and%20calcium%20are%20essential%20for%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20dev