e%20adds%20almost%202.7g%20of%20sugar%20in%20baby%20food%20like%20Cerelac%20in%20India.%20We%20spoke%20to%20experts%20to%20help%20young%20parents%20feed%20balanced%20and%20nutritious%20meals%20to%20babies%20and%20toddlers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Ace%20The%20UPSC%20CSE%20Personality%20Test%3F%20IAS%20Officer%20With%20AIR%207%20Shares%20Tips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20morning%20of%2030%20May%2C%202022%2C%20is%20still%20a%20blur%20of%20memory%20for%20Delhi%20resident%20Samyak%20Jain.%20It%20was%20the%20day%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337399%2Fbihar-ias-officer-anshuman-raj-cracked-upsc-cse-without-coaching-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20exam%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20set%20to%20be%20declared.%20As%20Samyak%20and%20his%20parents%20gathered%20around%20the%20computer%20screen%2C%20refreshing%20it%20multiple%20times%20eager%20to%20watch%20the%20score%20reflect%2C%20a%20million%20thoughts%20were%20racing%20through%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20my%20name%20feature%20in%20the%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samyak%20shares%20what%20he%20was%20praying%20for%20during%20those%20moments%20of%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20later%2C%20tears%20of%20joy%20and%20happiness%20were%20being%20shed%20as%20a%20shocked%20Samyak%20still%20grappled%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20had%20scored%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20(AIR)%207.%20Anticipating%20to%20feature%20in%20the%20top%20100%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cawesome%E2%80%9D%20thought%3B%20believing%20he%20would%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%2010%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunthinkable%E2%80%9D.%20It%20seemed%20too%20far-fetched%20for%20the%20young%20aspirant.%20Double-checking%20and%20triple-checking%20convinced%20Samyak%20that%20the%20score%20was%20indeed%20