C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCwhRO7PvlGM%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Samyak%20Jain%20IAS%20(%40samyakjain.ias)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlways%20set%20a%20high%20target%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CReach%20for%20the%20moon.%20If%20you%20miss%20it%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20land%20among%20the%20stars%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20borrowing%20from%20this%20philosophy%2C%20Samyak%20says%20in%20his%20second%20attempt%2C%20he%20kept%20the%20general%20category%20cut-off%20as%20his%20goal%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20PwD%20(persons%20with%20disabilities)%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20PwD%20category%20has%20a%20lower%20cut-off%20than%20the%20general.%20In%20my%20first%20attempt%2C%20I%20had%20noticed%20this%20and%20was%20trying%20to%20match%20this%20cut-off.%20But%2C%20in%20my%20second%20attempt%2C%20I%20learnt%20from%20my%20mistake%20and%20aimed%20for%20the%20general%20category%20cut-off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20a%20holy%20grail%20for%20your%20optional%20subject%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreparing%20for%20the%20UPSC%20is%20often%20viewed%20as%20nerve-racking%20by%20the%20many%20aspirants%20who%20attempt%20it%20every%20year.%20But%20a%20foolproof%20plan%20is%20what%20will%20differentiate%20you%20from%20others%2C%20believes%20Samyak.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307829%2Frevision-tips-for-upsc-cse-mains-optional-subject-by-ias-officer-akshita-gupta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echoosing%20an%20optional%20subject%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20recommends%20going%20for%20something%20that%20you%20are%20passionate%20about%20and%20know%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20from%20JNU%20(Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi)%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20Samyak%20choosing%20political%20science%20and%20international%20relations%20as%20his%20optional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotes%20formed%20the%20bedrock%20of%20his%20preparation%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20political%20science%20paper%2C%20Samyak%20says%20it%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20parts%2C%20with%20each%20part%20featuring%20two%20sections.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20sections%2C%20three%20are%20static%20(a%20set%20of%20questions%20that%20repeat%20over%20the%20years)%20and%20one%20is%20dynamic%20(questions%20that%20assess%20your%20knowledge%20of%20current%20affairs%20and%20news).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20static%20sections%2C%20going%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277424%2Fbest-books-for-upsc-cse-indian-polity-laxmikanth-amazon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20years%E2%80%99%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20suffices%2C%20Samyak%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20bank%20(of%20notes)%20has%20around%202%2C500%20questions%20that%20feature%20ad%20verbatim%2C%20with%20a%20few%20changes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20This%20leaves%20a%20candidate%20with%20the%20fourth%20section%20on%20which%20they%20must%20spend%20adequate%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20section%20is%20more%20challenging%20than%20the%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samyak%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoaching%20might%20not%20be%20your%20cup%20of%20tea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamyak%20once%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20become%20an%20engineer.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20phase%20when%20he%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20IIT%20exam%20that%20he%20attended%20coaching%20classes.%20However%2C%20he%20instantly%20knew%20this%20style%20of%20learning%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20suited%20to%20his%20temperament.%20Thus%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20UPSC%20exam%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20study%20by%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20wanting%20to%20dissuade%20anyone%20from%20opting%20for%20coaching%2C%20Samyak%20emphasises%20it%20merely%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20his%20cup%20of%20tea.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20each%20his%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcing%20the%20final%20frontier%20%E2%80%94%20the%20personality%20test%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20daunting%20UPSC%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20the%20interview%20round%20more%20famously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPersonality%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20is%20actually%20designed%20to%20test%20one%E2%80%99s%20integrity%2C%20Samyak%20emphasises.%20Take%20its%20name%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20in%20every%20interview%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20five-minute%20or%2010-minute%20period%20when%20the%20candidate%20is%20grilled%20and%20might%20find%20themselves%20on%20the%20spot.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20get%20anxious%20or%20fidget%20with%20your%20hands%20during%20this%20time.%20The%20examiners%20are%20trying%20to%20assess%20how%20well%20you%20perform%20in%20real-time%20high-pressure%20situations.%20They%20are%20not%20testing%20your%20knowledge%20but%20rather%20your%20personality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20his%20own%20interview%2C%20he%20shares%20how%20a%20casual%20mention%20of%20%E2%80%98yellow%20journalism%E2%80%99%20in%20one%20of%20his%20answers%20led%20him%20to%20be%20questioned%20about%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20to%20dodge%20the%20question%20a%20few%20times.%20But%20eventually%2C%20the%20examiner%20asked%20me%20a%20pointed%20question%20as%20to%20what%20I%20meant%20and%20I%20had%20to%20explain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorrowing%20from%20this%20incident%2C%20he%20says%20there%20will%20be%20times%20when%20candidates%20can%20be%20expected%20to%20be%20bombarded%20with%20questions%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20keep%20calm%20and%20composed%20as%20you%20speak%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091-500x683.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samyak%20Jain%2C%20who%20began%20losing%20his%20vision%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20secured%20an%20AIR%207%20in%20his%20second%20attempt%20of%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20exam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091-500x683.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091-220x300.jpg%20220w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091-150x205.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FScreenshot-2024-04-17-115409-1713335091.jpg%20574w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESamyak%20Jain%2C%20who%20began%20losing%20his%20vision%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20secured%20an%20AIR%207%20in%20his%20second%20attempt%20of%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%20exam%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Samyak%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20it%20seems%20impossible%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20doing%20it%20wrong%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Samyak%20began%20losing%20his%20vision%2C%20his%20journey%20has%20been%20fraught%20with%20m