g%20techniques.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20used%20to%20grow%20strawberries%20on%20the%20open%20farm%20on%20five%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20was%20very%20cumbersome%20as%20it%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20land%2C%20mulching%2C%20and%20drip%20irrigation.%20Weeding%20is%20also%20a%20common%20issue%20in%20growing%20strawberries%20on%20land.%20To%20get%20rid%20of%20the%20unwanted%20grass%2C%20we%20had%20to%20employ%20agricultural%20labourers.%20The%20labour%20charges%20alone%20would%20cost%20us%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20remove%20weeds%20from%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dheeraj%2C%20hydroponics%20farming%20seemed%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20went%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20undertake%20training%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhakad%20Brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20the%20hydroponics%20method%20of%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20hydroponics%20farming%2C%20you%20give%20nutrients%20to%20plants%20via%20water.%20A%20crop%20requires%2013%20kinds%20of%20nutrients%20including%20primary%20nutrients%20like%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20and%20potassium%2C%20secondary%20nutrients%20like%20calcium%2C%20sulphur%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%20and%20tertiary%20nutrients%20like%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20manganese%2C%20copper%2C%20boron%2C%20molybdenum%2C%20and%20chlorine.%20These%20elements%20act%20as%20an%20essential%20catalyst%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20knew%20the%20technique%20to%20give%20these%20nutrients%20via%20water%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20the%20ratio%20in%20which%20these%20elements%20were%20required%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20crop.%20The%20training%20helped%20