0crop%20with%20water.%20With%20this%20method%2C%20I%20water%20the%20plant%20at%20a%20gap%20of%20a%20week%2C%20instead%20of%20running%20the%20water%20supply%2024%C3%977.%20Almost%2070%20percent%20of%20water%20gets%20absorbed%20in%20the%20media%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Dheeraj%201.5%20months%20and%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20to%20build%20the%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20all%20worth%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment%20that%20reduces%20the%20overall%20input%20costs%20after%20a%20certain%20period.%20For%20five%20years%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries%20and%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20method%20is%20far%20better%20than%20conventional%20farming.%20With%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20got%20five%20times%20more%20production%20in%20hydroponics%20compared%20to%20open-land%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20tasks%20farmers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20while%20adopting%20this%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20hydroponics%20farm%20at%20least%20once%20every%20day.%20The%20strawberries%20are%20heavily%20attacked%20by%20pests%20and%20fungus.%20In%20land-based%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20spray%20chemical%20pesticides%20indiscriminately.%20But%20in%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20cut%20chemical%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20this%20year%2